Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:01.60,Default_Top,NTP,0,0,0,,OPEN THE NEW TALE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:05.22,Default_Top,NTP,0,0,0,,揃って旅に出かける
